Setting Circles Profiles
Circles avatars are ERC‑1155 tokens whose metadata field points to an IPFS CID. The JSON stored at that CID contains the human-friendly profile (name, description, images, etc.) that explorers and UIs render.
```
@aboutcircles/sdk
```
exposes helpers on every avatar instance, while
```
@aboutcircles/sdk-profiles
```
provides you a lightweight client for direct pin/get calls.
