Updating On-Chain Metadata
For avatars you control:
Pin the JSON:
```
const cid = await avatar.profile.update(profileData);
```
The helper converts the CIDv0 into the bytes32 digest (
```
cidV0ToHex
```
) and submits
```
nameRegistry.updateMetadataDigest
```
Subsequent reads pull the updated profile, and you can register short names via
```
avatar.profile.registerShortName(nonce)
```
if desired.
You can also skip the pinning step when you already have a CID:
Copy
```
await avatar.profile.updateMetadata('QmExampleCidV0');
```
